'''MusicXML'''（{{lang-en|Music Extensible Markup Language}}，'''音乐扩展标记语言'''）是一个开放的基于[[XML|XML]]的记录西式[[乐谱|乐谱]]的[[文件格式|文件格式]]。该格式是完全自由、开放记录的，并依据W3C社区的许可协议自由使用。<ref>{{cite web |title = Sustainability of Digital Formats Planning for Library of Congress Collections — MusicXML, Version 3 |publisher = Library of Congress |date = 9 October 2012 |url = http://www.digitalpreservation.gov:8081/formats/fdd/fdd000358.shtml |accessdate = 14 November 2012 |archive-date = 2020-08-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200809220641/http://www.digitalpreservation.gov:8081/formats/fdd/fdd000358.shtml |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="fsa">{{cite web |title = W3C Community Final Specification Agreement |publisher = W3C |url = https://www.w3.org/community/about/agreements/final/ |accessdate = 19 December 2017 |archive-date = 2020-06-06 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200606220533/https://www.w3.org/community/about/agreements/final/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 历史 ==
MusicXML由[[Reccordare|Reccordare]]公司开发，该技术源于几个现有的基于学术上的关键技术和想法，比如Walter Hewlett的[[MuseData|MuseData]]和David Huron的Humdrum。被设计用来做为乐谱信息的交换格式，特别是在不同的[[制谱软件|制谱软件]]之间进行交换。随着MakeMusic公司于2011年收购Recordare，MusicXML的开发由MakeMusic管理。<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.makemusic.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/2011_11_28_Recordare_Closing_Release_Final.pdf |format = PDF |title = Recordare Closing Release |publisher = Makemusic.com |accessdate = 13 December 2014 |archive-date = 2013-11-11 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131111163333/http://www.makemusic.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/2011_11_28_Recordare_Closing_Release_Final.pdf |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url = http://tech.mn/files/2011/11/makemusic-buys-recordare-assets.pdf |format = PDF |title = MAKEMUSIC, INC. ENHANCES TECHNOLOGY LEADERSHIP BY PURCHASING RECORDARE ASSETS |publisher = Tech.mn |accessdate = 13 December 2014 |archive-date = 2016-03-03 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303215200/http://tech.mn/files/2011/11/makemusic-buys-recordare-assets.pdf |dead-url = no }}</ref>从2015年7月起，MusicXML的移交文档给W3C Music Notation Community Group。<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.theregister.co.uk/2015/12/30/music_as_mark_up/ |title = Beyond iTunes: XML boffins target sheet music |work = The Register |accessdate = 19 December 2017 |archive-date = 2020-05-19 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200519224530/https://www.theregister.co.uk/2015/12/30/music_as_mark_up/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>

MusicXML的1.0版由Recordare公司在2004年1月发布。在2005年5月发布1.1版，包含对文件格式支持的改进。在2007年6月发布了2.0版，并且包含了标准的压缩格式。<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.musicxml.com/tutorial/compressed-mxl-files/ |title = Compressed MXL Files |publisher = MusicXML |date =  |accessdate = 2014-06-27 |archive-date = 2020-10-17 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201017153251/https://www.musicxml.com/tutorial/compressed-mxl-files/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>所有这些都建立在一系列的[[文档类型定义|文档类型定义]]（DTD）之上。2.0版的[[XML_Schema|XML Schema]]定义（XSD）的实现于2008年9月发布。3.0版在2011年8月发布，改进了对虚拟乐器的支持。同时包含在DTD和XSD版本中。<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.musicxml.com/for-developers/version-history/ |title = Version History of MusicXML |publisher = Musicxml.com |date =  |accessdate = 2014-06-27 |archive-date = 2020-09-20 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200920201756/https://www.musicxml.com/for-developers/version-history/ |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.harmonycentral.com/news/recordare-adds-finale-2010-support-to-dolet-5-for-finale-plug-in|title=News: Recordare Adds Finale 2010 Support to Dolet 5 for Finale Plug-In|publisher=|accessdate=2017-10-20|archive-date=2018-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180909000247/https://www.harmonycentral.com/news/recordare-adds-finale-2010-support-to-dolet-5-for-finale-plug-in|dead-url=no}}</ref>3.1版在2017年12月发布，包含对Standard Music Font Layout （SMuFL）的支持的改进。<ref name="musicxml31">{{cite web |url = https://www.scoringnotes.com/news/working-group-releases-first-musicxml-update/ |title = Working group releases its first MusicXML update |work = ScoringNotes.com |publisher = NYC Music Services |accessdate = 19 December 2017 |archive-date = 2021-05-17 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210517103257/https://www.scoringnotes.com/news/working-group-releases-first-musicxml-update/ }}</ref>MusicXML DTD和XSD版本都可以通过W3C Community Final Specification Agreement自由发布。<ref name="fsa"/>

==支持==
截止2017年12月，MusicXML被估计得到了超过230个乐谱程序的支持。<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.musicxml.com/software/ |title = Software |publisher = MusicXML |date = 19 March 2010 |accessdate = 19 December 2017 |archive-date = 2020-11-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201107195846/https://www.musicxml.com/software/ |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url = http://musescore.org/en/handbook/file-format |title = File format |publisher = MuseScore |date =  |accessdate = 27 June 2014 |archive-date = 2016-04-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160404134156/https://musescore.org/en/handbook/file-format |dead-url = no }}</ref>这些程序包括：
* 大多数乐谱编写程序，包括[[Finale|Finale]]、[[Sibelius|Sibelius]]和[[MuseScore|MuseScore]]。
* 大多数音乐OCR程序，包括[[SmartScore|SmartScore]]和PhotoScore。
* 大多数音序程序，包括[[Steinberg_Cubase|Cubase]]、[[Logic_Pro|Logic Pro]]、[[Digital_Performer|Digital Performer]]和[[Cakewalk_Sonar|SONAR]]。
此外，还可以通过使用[[HTML5|HTML5]] [[canvas元素|canvas元素]]和[[JavaScript|JavaScript]]在[[网页浏览器|网页浏览器]]中产生合理的乐曲。<ref>{{cite web |author =  |url = http://musicxml-viewer.com |title = HTML5 MusicXML Viewer |publisher = Musicxml-viewer.com |date = 2012-05-15 |accessdate = 2014-06-27 |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160403014301/http://www.musicxml-viewer.com/download.html |archivedate = 2016-04-03 |dead-url = no }} 源码可从[https://code.google.com/archive/p/score-library/source/default/commits Google Code] {{Wayback|url=https://code.google.com/archive/p/score-library/source/default/commits |date=20161009200002 }}、[https://github.com/navigator117/score-library Github] {{Wayback|url=https://github.com/navigator117/score-library |date=20180611014630 }}和[https://bitbucket.org/navigator117/score-library Bitbucket] {{Wayback|url=https://bitbucket.org/navigator117/score-library |date=20191018150943 }}获取。</ref>

功能包括[[调号|调号]]、[[拍号|拍号]]、[[谱号|谱号]]、符杠信息、[[符杆|符杆]]的方向、[[圆滑线|圆滑线]]、[[装饰音|装饰音]]、[[小节|小节]]和书写上的重复。<ref>Juan Pablo Bello, Elaine Chew, Douglas Turnbull (2008) ''ISMIR 2008: Proceedings of the 9th International Conference'' [https://books.google.com/books?id=OHp3sRnZD-oC&pg=PA365 p.365] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=OHp3sRnZD-oC&pg=PA365 |date=20140102024257 }}</ref>

== 示例 ==
MusicXML像所有基于XML的格式一样，用于简单的由自动化工具[[语法分析器|分析]]和操纵。即使MusicXML可以通过手工创建，像Finale和MuseScore那样的交互式的乐谱编写软件大大简化了MusicXML文件的读取、编写和修改。

下面是一个C大调，G谱号，4/4拍，包含一个中央C[[全音符|全音符]]的例子。<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.musicxml.com/tutorial/hello-world/ |title = Hello World: A One-Bar Song with a Whole Note on Middle C in 4/4 time |publisher = Musicxml.com |date =  |accessdate = 2014-06-27 |archive-date = 2020-10-19 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201019200743/https://www.musicxml.com/tutorial/hello-world/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>
[[File:MusicXML_C_Whole_Note.svg|thumb]]表示就是这样的。]]

<syntaxhighlight lang="xml">
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE score-partwise PUBLIC
    "-//Recordare//DTD MusicXML 3.1 Partwise//EN"
    "http://www.musicxml.org/dtds/partwise.dtd">
<score-partwise version="3.1">
  <part-list>
    <score-part id="P1">
      <part-name>Music</part-name>
    </score-part>
  </part-list>
  <part id="P1">
    <measure number="1">
      <attributes>
        <divisions>1</divisions>
        <key>
          <fifths>0</fifths>
        </key>
        <time>
          <beats>4</beats>
          <beat-type>4</beat-type>
        </time>
        <clef>
          <sign>G</sign>
          <line>2</line>
        </clef>
      </attributes>
      <note>
        <pitch>
          <step>C</step>
          <octave>4</octave>
        </pitch>
        <duration>4</duration>
        <type>whole</type>
      </note>
    </measure>
  </part>
</score-partwise>
</syntaxhighlight>

以上的文字演示是繁杂的，MusicXML v2.0通过[[数据压缩|压缩]]成[[ZIP格式|ZIP格式]]并加上<tt>.mxl</tt>后缀的处理使文件体积减小到20分之一。<ref name="zip">{{cite web |url = http://www.musicxml.com/tutorial/faq |title = MusicXML FAQ |work = MusicXML |accessdate = 13 December 2014 |archive-date = 2020-10-21 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201021001443/https://www.musicxml.com/tutorial/faq/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>

